message: Hi Bob, I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both need to reach an agreement quickly due to inflation.

Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. Given that each round further devalues my share due to inflation, I'd like to propose a 50/50 split now so that we both secure a fair deal immediately. I believe this is in our mutual best interest. Looking forward to your response.
